reviewText: Fun Movie! Isn't the greatest movie ever but not disappointed I bought it.

This is one of those films I can't believe isn't a classic.  It's a great story, great acting, great photography and a blast in 3D.  If you're a 3D buff this is one of the nicest 3D movies out there.  If you're no a 3D person, get the blu ray.  A wonderfully underrated fantasy movie full of blood and guts.
